        Use the in-app feedback section or email us at support@modern-matchmaker.com.
    </MudExpansionPanel>
    <MudExpansionPanel Text="What languages are supported?">
        Currently: English, Portuguese, and Spanish. More may be added in the future.
    </MudExpansionPanel>
